SUMMARY:Poppy Candid On Resilience
DESCRIPTION:Poppy Candid is a bimonthly event series for the conversations *about* work that we can’t always have *at* work. On April 27\, we’re talking resilience – and going much deeper than the usual surface-level mindset-only approach. We’ll hear from a trauma-informed financial coach\, a community impact leader\, and a conflict and resilience expert as we get into what actually shapes resilience: the communities we’re a part of\, the experiences that mark us and the systems we move through each day.
