SUMMARY:SOLIDWORKS Hard-Tech Event
DESCRIPTION:SOLIDWORKS for Startups and the 3DEXPERIENCE Lab are hosting a startup meetup in downtown Seattle—and you’re invited! \n​Join us on Monday\, April 27\, from 6:00–8:30 PM PT for an evening of networking\, refreshments\, and great conversations with people building in the startup and hardware space. \n​You’ll have the chance to connect with founders\, innovators\, and industry leaders from both the local and global ecosystem. There will also be opportunities to participate in pitch competitions. \n​A night for founders\, fresh ideas\, and meaningful connections. Bring your energy and your questions\, and let’s light up the evening with discovery and fun! 🚀 \n​📲Location and agenda coming soon. \n​This hard-tech meetup kicks off the 30th anniversary celebration of the Seattle Area SOLIDWORKS Power Users Group\, which continues the next day\, April 28\, at the Museum of Flight. ✈️ \n​Join us from 2:00-7:00 PM PT for a free celebration of this SOLIDWORKS User Group network! \n​Register here! ⬅️🎉
