SUMMARY:Build Your AI Partnership: Collaboration by Design
DESCRIPTION:𝗢𝘃𝗲𝗿𝘃𝗶𝗲𝘄\nStop prompting. Start partnering. Build a structured AI collaboration framework that improves clarity\, speed\, and output quality.\nYou already use AI. But are you collaborating with it\, or just reacting to it? \nMost professionals treat AI like a search bar with better grammar. The result? Inconsistent outputs\, repeated context-setting\, vague goals\, drifting conversations\, and hours of rework that shouldn’t exist. \nThe problem isn’t the technology. It’s the missing structure around how you work with it. \n𝗖𝗼𝗹𝗹𝗮𝗯𝗼𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗯𝘆 𝗗𝗲𝘀𝗶𝗴𝗻 is a hands-on workshop that moves you from casual AI usage to intentional\, structured partnership. You’ll build a complete framework for how you and AI work together\, tailored to your role\, goals\, and working style. \n𝗪𝗵𝗮𝘁 𝗬𝗼𝘂’𝗹𝗹 𝗪𝗮𝗹𝗸 𝗔𝘄𝗮𝘆 𝗪𝗶𝘁𝗵:\n• A personalized Master Prompt that defines your role\, your AI partner’s role\, and how you interact\n• A clear method for setting intent and context before every AI engagement\n• The ability to detect and correct conversational drift before it costs you time\n• Structured interaction patterns that improve clarity\, speed\, and output quality\n• Confidence in maintaining human authority over accuracy\, ethics\, and final decisions \n𝗪𝗵𝗼 𝗧𝗵𝗶𝘀 𝗜𝘀 𝗙𝗼𝗿: \nKnowledge workers\, leaders\, consultants\, and professionals who use AI regularly and want to stop guessing and start operating with intention. \n𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗖𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗜𝗱𝗲𝗮: \nPerformance improves when relationship discipline improves. Clear expectations\, preserved context\, and intentional structure reduce cognitive load and rework\, while keeping you in control of judgment and creativity. \nThis isn’t a prompting tips session. It’s a working session where you build the system you’ll use every day.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/build-your-ai-partnership-collaboration-by-design/
LOCATION:The Pioneer Collective – West Canal Yards\, 1100 W Ewing Street\, Seattle\, 98119\, United States
CATEGORIES:Artificial Intelligence
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://cdn.geekwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Ai-with-Human-2.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Skills Leap":MAILTO:info@skillsleap.com
END:VEVENT
