SUMMARY:2026 AST Surgical Technology Conference
DESCRIPTION:Join us Sunday\, May 31 – Tuesday\, June 2\, 2026\, In Seattle\, Washington! Seattle offers iconic landmarks like the Space Needle\, a world-class coffee culture\, and a thriving tech scene. From exploring Pike Place Market to hiking in nearby national parks\, Seattle is a city that blends urban energy with outdoor adventure. Whether you’re a foodie\, artist\, entrepreneur\, or explorer\, Seattle welcomes you with open arms and endless possibilities. AST offers an event focused on education\, innovation\, and networking opportunities. It’s not just a professional gathering; it’s an opportunity to explore the unique charm and culture that Seattle has to offer. More information coming soon.
